group.pals.android.lib.ui.filechooser.utils.history
Class HistoryStore<A extends Parcelable>

java.lang.Object
  group.pals.android.lib.ui.filechooser.utils.history.HistoryStore<A>
All Implemented Interfaces:
History<A>
public class HistoryStore<A extends Parcelable>
extends Object
implements History<A>

A history store of any object extending Parcelable.
Note: This class does not support storing its HistoryListener 's into Parcelable. You must re-build all listeners after getting your HistoryStore from a Bundle for example.

Since:
v2.0 alpha
Author:
Hai Bison
